text: Clacton-on-Sea railway station is a railway station in England. It serves the town of Clacton-on-Sea in Essex. The station is near the town centre. It is within walking distance from the pier and sea. The station is on the Sunshine Coast Line. Services run to/from Colchester and Liverpool Street. ==References== Category:Railway stations in England Category:Tendring Category:1860 establishments in England Category:Buildings and structures in Essex
